{
  "stem": "10859.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I'm going to try and find something in a bigger city to do something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What could I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was not a professional, I mean, engineer or a lawyer or a doctor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I knew Hebrew well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I figured I'm going to go and take some private lessons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I got some private lessons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I could support myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I rent myself a room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't even live with my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was there, like, almost two years, from '37 till '39.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As you know, in '39, in September, the war broke out between Germany and Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not have any really connection with the Polish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because Polish people did not live around us, only Ukrainian people, Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Polish people, very few sometimes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the next little town, which I will mention this later, the name was Trochenbrod in Jewish, and in Polish, Sofievka.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the town there was some Polish people lived there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But not too many.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe there was 10 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was several thousand Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Those two little places was strictly Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't have really any connection to tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For another reason, if there was some anti-Semitism among the villages with Jewish people, with Ukrainian live together, or Jewish people with Polish people together, there's no question.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was always anti-Semitism only for jealousy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They couldn't see if the Jewish people lived nice or they have a nice home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But our place, everybody was so poor, they couldn't be jealous of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we didn't fight with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't fight with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we lived as good neighbors I could say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was a very good person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She never was interested to get married.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
